rows.label: qev070307_MSG0002
rows.name: not Professor B. *sigh* Where IS he?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070307_MSG0003
rows.name:
Disaster... Ruination... Despair... Apocalypse...
So many words dance through my mind and melt
away as I sit here waiting for Professor B.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070307_MSG0004
rows.name:
What in the world possessed me to let such a clearly
suspicious xeno buy that many parts on credit?
Regret... Hopelessness... Perdition...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070307_MSG0005
rows.name: You saved Professor B? Oh, thank you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev070307_MSG0006
rows.name:
If he hadn't come back, I would have had to quietly
disappear from New LA as well...[ST:wait ]
